sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Route as task.route.ts
    participant Middleware as Middleware
    participant Controller as task.controller.ts
    participant Service as task.service.ts
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant MongoDB as MongoDB
    participant Socket as Socket.io
    participant Queue as BullMQ

    Note over User,Queue: Task Creation Flow V2 (Family-Based)

    User->>Route: POST /tasks<br/>{title, taskType, assignedUserIds}
    Route->>Middleware: authenticate()
    Middleware-->>Route: User ID

    Route->>Middleware: checkSecondaryUserPermission()
    Middleware->>MongoDB: Check ChildrenBusinessUser
    MongoDB-->>Middleware: Secondary User Status
    Middleware-->>Route: Permission Granted/Denied

    Route->>Middleware: validateTaskTypeConsistency()
    Route->>Middleware: checkDailyTaskLimit()
    Route->>Controller: create()

    Controller->>Service: createTask(data, userId)
    Service->>Redis: Check Cache (skip)
    Redis-->>Service: Cache Miss

    Service->>MongoDB: Insert Task Document
    MongoDB-->>Service: Created Task

    alt Collaborative Task
        Service->>Service: Record Family Activity
        Service->>Socket: broadcastToFamilyMembers()
        Socket-->>User: Real-time Task Created Event
    end

    Service->>Redis: Invalidate User Cache Keys
    Redis-->>Service: Cache Invalidated

    Service-->>Controller: Task Created
    Controller-->>User: 201 Created<br/>{task, message}

    Note over User,Queue: Task Status Update Flow

    User->>Route: PUT /tasks/:id/status<br/>{status: "completed"}
    Route->>Middleware: verifyTaskAccess()
    Route->>Middleware: validateStatusTransition()
    Route->>Controller: updateStatus()

    Controller->>Service: updateTaskStatus(taskId, status, userId)
    Service->>MongoDB: Update Task Status<br/>Set completedTime
    MongoDB-->>Service: Updated Task

    alt Collaborative Task
        Service->>Service: Record Family Activity
        Service->>Socket: broadcastToFamilyMembers()
        Socket-->>User: Real-time Status Changed Event
    end

    Service->>Redis: Invalidate Cache
    Redis-->>Service: Cache Invalidated

    Service->>Queue: Add preferredTimeQueue Job<br/>JobId: preferred-time:userId:timestamp
    Queue-->>Service: Job Queued

    Service-->>Controller: Status Updated
    Controller-->>User: 200 OK<br/>{task, message}

    Note over User,Queue: Get Tasks with Pagination

    User->>Route: GET /tasks/paginate?<br/>page=1&limit=10&status=pending
    Route->>Middleware: authenticate()
    Route->>Middleware: validateFiltersForQuery()
    Route->>Controller: getMyTasksWithPagination()

    Controller->>Service: getUserTasksWithPagination(userId, filters, options)
    Service->>Redis: Check Cache
    Redis-->>Service: Cache Miss

    Service->>MongoDB: Find with Pagination<br/>Query: {ownerUserId, status, isDeleted}
    MongoDB-->>Service: Paginated Tasks

    Service->>Redis: Cache Results<br/>TTL: 120 seconds
    Redis-->>Service: Cached

    Service-->>Controller: Paginated Response
    Controller-->>User: 200 OK<br/>{tasks, meta, pagination}

    Note over User,Queue: Daily Progress Flow

    User->>Route: GET /tasks/daily-progress?date=2026-03-14
    Route->>Controller: getDailyProgress()
    Controller->>Service: getDailyProgress(userId, date)

    Service->>Redis: Check Daily Cache
    Redis-->>Service: Cache Miss

    Service->>MongoDB: Find Tasks for Date<br/>startTime: startOfDay - endOfDay
    MongoDB-->>Service: Today's Tasks

    Service->>Service: Calculate Statistics<br/>Total, Completed, In Progress, %
    Service->>Redis: Cache Results<br/>TTL: 120 seconds
    Redis-->>Service: Cached

    Service-->>Controller: Daily Progress Data
    Controller-->>User: 200 OK<br/>{date, total, completed, progressPercentage, tasks}
